vity. Five H II regions show evidence of outflows which are most\nlikely supported by either stellar winds (2 regions) or champagne flows (3\nregions). These observations provide new insights into the state of the\nstar-forming regions in IC 10 and negative feedback from low mass clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Feb 2022 19:02:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
