ated without a defined period. On a global\nscale, the cortex dynamically alternated among high and low complex states.\nThis study brings novel evidence of the effects of anesthetics on neural\nactivity and cortical dynamics, complementing the actual scenario for the\nelucidation of anesthesia mechanisms in terms of circuits, pathways, and global\nbrain functioning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 08:04:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-10"}
