, and minimal charge disorder, but can\nalso protect the TMD from irradiation damage. This work provides a better\nunderstanding of the mechanisms by which \\textit{h}-BN remains, to date, the\nmost compatible material for 2D material encapsulation, facilitating the\nrealization of intrinsic material properties to their full potential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 14:31:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
